title: Flowmaster American Thunder Axle-back Exhaust System for 2016 Camaro LT w/ 2.0L Turbo - 817751
description:
Flowmaster's American Thunder Axle-back for '16 Camaro LT (Coupe and Convertible) w/ 2.0L turbo - Part # 817751

Flowmaster Part # 817751

Application:
Fits 2016 Camaro LT with 2.0L Engine. Does NOT Fit Vehicles Fitted With Performance Exhaust Option (Quad Tip).

Features:
Flowmaster's American Thunder® Axle-back exhaust system for the 2016 Camaro LT (Coupe and Convertible) with the 2.0L turbocharged engine, is perfect for the person looking for a moderate sound level both inside and outside of the car, with all of the performance benefits you would expect from Flowmaster. This bolt-on DOR (Dual Out Rear) emissions-legal system features a pair of free flowing Outlaw® Series mufflers and dual mandrel bent 2.50 inch tailpipes for maximum performance. The system is built out of 409S stainless steel and utilizes 4.00 inch polished stainless steel tips. The exhaust system is manufactured in the USA and covered by Flowmaster's Lifetime Limited Warranty. Designed for an easy fit, this system includes all necessary parts and hardware for installation.

-Stainless Steel Construction
-Dyno Tuned For Maximum Performance
-Mandrel Bent Tubing

Please call 707-544-4761 or visit http://www.flowmastermufflers.com for additional application and product information.
